I have two accounts, but I hadn't attempted to 2 box until recently.<br>
<br>
I decided on an enchanter, so I started one on my second account.<br>
<br>
TWO weeks later he was 51st level, and not lacking on any of his skills.<br>
<br>
I couldn't imagine a better combo than a magician PL'ing an enchanter.<br>
<br>
Mage pet attacks a mob.  Enchanter mez'es the mob at 5-10%.  Enchanter memory blurs.  Enchanter nukes mob.  Enchanter gets MUCHO experience.<br>
