<br>
Magician 2-boxing with Magician.<br>
<br>
Did it with two, now I do it with 3.  <br>
<br>
Slow and mez and heal are great but imagine chain casting two pets.<br>
<br>
I did Priest of Discord just for the fun of it.  This guy has high magic resist.  I tried fire and magic based nukes and couldn't touch him.  So I started chaining Dizzy pets on all 3 magicians.  Kept two on PoD at all times giving 3rd chance to DS himself.  If he didn't, I would throw DS on him.  Then I just let PoD kill himself on DS.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>My</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> biggest justification for using Magician on both accounts is because it is easier.  Same spells and same set up on both. <br>
<br>
That's just me.  Not a popular view but one worth considering. <p><BR>I AM DZR <BR>

